in]]\"\n|[[Eruption (band)|Eruption]] featuring [[Precious Wilson]]\n| align=\"center\" | 5\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 43\n| \"[[Mr. Blue Sky]]\"\n| Electric Light Orchestra\n| align=\"center\" | 6\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 44\n| \"[[Uptown Top Ranking]]\"\n| [[Althia and Donna]]\n| align=\"center\" | 1\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 45\n| \"[[MacArthur Park (song)|MacArthur Park]]\"\n| {{Sortname|Donna|Summer}}\n| align=\"center\" | 5\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 46\n| \"[[I Wonder Why]]\"\n| [[Showaddywaddy]]\n| align=\"center\" | 2\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 47\n| \"[[You Make Me Feel (Mighty Real)]]\"\n| [[Sylvester (singer)|Sylvester]]\n| align=\"center\" | 8\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 48\n| \"If You Can't Give Me Love\"\n| {{Sortname|Suzi|Quatro}}\n| align=\"center\" | 4\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 49\n| \"A Taste of Aggro\"\n| {{Sortname|The|Barron Knights}}\n| align=\"center\" | 3\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 50\n| \"[[Forever Autumn (song)|Forever Autumn]]\"\n| {{Sortname|Justin|Hayward}}\n| align=\"center\" | 5\n|}\n\n===Best-selling albums===\n<ref>Scaping (1979). \"Top 200 LPs in 1978\". pp. 182\u201385.</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n!scope=col| {{Abbr|No.|Number}}\n!scope=col| Title\n!scope=col| Artist\n!scope=col| Peak<br />position\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1\n| ''[[Saturday Night Fever (album)|Saturday Night Fever]]''\n| Original Soundtrack\n| align=\"center\" | 1\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2\n| ''[[Grease: The Original Soundtrack from the Motion Picture|Grease]]''\n| Original Soundtrack\n| align=\"center\" | 1\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 3\n| ''[[The Album (ABBA album)|The Album]]''\n| [[ABBA]]\n| align=\"center\" | 1\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align:center;\"| 4\n| ''[[Nightflight to Venus]]''\n| [[Boney M]]\n| align=\"cent