-5382 |ref=harv }}\n* {{cite book|last1=Williams |first1=Martin F. |last2=Lowe |first2=Derek J. |title=The Bala Branch |year=2018 |publisher=Lightmoor Press |location=[[Lydney]] |isbn=978-1-91103-847-4 |ref=harv}}\n{{refend}}\n==Further material==\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book|last=Baughan |first= Peter E.|date=1980 |edition=1st |title=A Regional History of the Railways of Great Britain: Volume 11 North and Mid Wales |location=[[Newton Abbot]] | publisher=[[David & Charles]] |isbn=978-0-7153-7850-2 |oclc=6823219 |ref=harv }}\n* {{cite DVD |last1=Ferris |first1=Tom |title=British Railways Volume 4 - Bewdley To Blaenau |medium=DVD |year= 2004 |origyear=1961 |publisher=demanddvd |location= |isbn= |id= DEMDVD084|ref=harv }}\n* {{cite book |last=Turner |first=Alun |title=Gwynedd's Lost Railways |year=2003 |publisher=Stenlake Publishing |location=[[Catrine]] |isbn=978-1-84033-259-9 |ref=harv }}\n{{refend}}\n==External links==\n*{{cite web |url=http://maps.nls.uk/geo/explore/#zoom=16&lat=52.9700&lon=-3.9216&layers=10&b=1 |title=The station site on a navigable OS Map |website=National Library of Scotland }}\n*{{cite web |url=http://www.npemap.org.uk/tiles/map.html#270,342,1 |title=The station on a navigable 1953 OS map |website=npe Maps }}\n*{{cite web |url=http://www.RailMapOnline.com/UKIEMap.php?lat=52.96950&lng=-3.91878 |title=The station and line |website=Rail Map Online }}\n*{{cite web |url=http://www.railwaycodes.org.uk/elrs/_mileages/L/LJT2.txt |title=The line LJT2 with mileages |website=Railway Codes }}\n*{{cite web| url=http://www.forgottenrelics.co.uk/films/railrems.html |title=Reminiscences by a local railwayman |website=Forgotten Relics }}\n*{{cite web| url=http://www.catskillarchive.com/rrextra/stfest.Html |title=An American's tour of the FR and F&BR in 1873 |website=Catskill Archive }}\n*{{cite web| url=https://www.festipedia.org.uk/wiki/Festiniog_and_Blaenau_Railway |title=Festiniog and Blaenau Railway |website=Festipedia }}\n\n{{Closed stations Gwynedd}}\n\n[